</mediaobject></screenshot>
</figure></para>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>Properties and values: This is where you will find all the <acronym>CSS</acronym> dialogs for properties and values.</para>
<para>It contains 66 dialogs to ease <acronym>CSS</acronym> creation either aural, visual, or paged.</para>
<para><figure float="0" id="figure-csspropertiesmenu">
<title id="figure-csspropertiesmenu-title"><acronym>CSS</acronym> Properties and Values menu</title>
<screenshot><mediaobject>
