<textobject><phrase>The <acronym>CSS</acronym> Properties and Values menu</phrase></textobject>
</mediaobject></screenshot>
</figure></para>
<para>Each item leads to another cascade of submenus, to finally end up with access to a given dialog.</para>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>Here you can see the path to the border width style and color item:</para>
<para><figure float="0" id="figure-cssbordermenu">
