<listitem>
<para>Wizards: box properties, selector, and color for complex rules</para>
<para>This is where you go when you have complex properties to build.</para>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<para>The box properties wizard allows you to set values for margin, padding, border, and box size properties.</para>
<para>It is made of three parts:</para>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
