<imageobject><imagedata fileref="figures/boxwizard2.png" format="PNG"></imageobject>
<textobject><phrase>Shorthand properties in Box Properties wizard</phrase></textobject>
</mediaobject></screenshot>
</figure></para>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<para>The third part is a quick help for you to locate quickly the various concepts in a <acronym>CSS</acronym> box.</para>
<para><figure float="0" id="figure-boxwizard3">
<title id="figure-boxwizard3-title">Quick help in Box Properties wizard</title>
